                                            Forget all the other years; this year will be the year of the Linux desktop.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>The year of the Linux desktop may be a bit of a joke, but switching to Linux is not. You've either done it at some point, or you're probably considering it. Linux is quickly improving, while Windows is increasingly becoming hostile. I've outlined four ways that Linux will gain ground on Windows.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Sat, 13 Sep 2025 11:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/linux-vs-windows-why-linux-will-gain-ground-in-the-desktop-war/</guid></item></channel>
